'Coldspot' is a term used to describe an area or space free from electromagnetic activity. It can be used more specifically to highlight an area free from wireless internet known as ‘wi-fi’.It was first coined by the Wavefighters organization in 2005 as the antithetical rival to ‘hot-spots’. Coldspots can be created by using Faraday cage technology.
[http://www.wavefighters.org/coldspot.htm]

